Ask HN: Share Embedded GPT Model Without Going Broke?
text:
Hey,

I'm looking to share an embedded GPT Model that I've been working on after I was kind of inspired by the Paul Graham Model(https://paul-graham-gpt.vercel.app/) by @mckaywrigley. The problem is that every API call costs money and @mckaywrigley solved it by asking for people's OpenAI API Key to talk to the model, which a lot of non-technical people don't get. Also, I know you can put a limit on your OpenAI Account so your bill isn't astronomical the next day but that kind of defeats the purpose of sharing it online. Hopefully, there's a solution but if not I'll just ask for API Keys too.
